### Seasonal Suitability API - Test Requests
### Use the REST Client extension in VS Code or copy to Postman

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/seasonal-suitability/health

###

### Get Prediction - Good Conditions (July in Idukki)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/seasonal-suitability/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "month": 7,
  "district": "Idukki",
  "pincode": 685501,
  "variety": "Panniyur 5",
  "temperature": 24.5,
  "rainfall": 320,
  "humidity": 82,
  "waterAvailability": "High"
}

###

