### Get Analytics Summary
GET http://localhost:5000/api/seasonal-suitability/analytics/summary

###

### Get Variety-wise Analytics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/seasonal-suitability/analytics/by-variety

###

### Track User Action (after getting a prediction)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/seasonal-suitability/track-action
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "analyticsId": "YOUR_ANALYTICS_ID_FROM_PREDICTION",
  "actionType": "addedToCart"
}
